{
  "stem": "19921.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 490.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was so dense that you couldn't see nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in that forest, actually, we had bears and wolves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were living in that area there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But in any event, we were assigned to take those trees down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And each one has different assignment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so, that's what we were doing-- taking down those trees manually, because no electric saws, no any technique.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They just put on a foreman, which was also a KBG man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he showed us how to do it, and he teached us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You look at the top of the tree, he said, and see in what direction that tree leans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that tree has to go that direction.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You don't cut the tree in the opposite direction, because it goes on your head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So that's-- that was the lessons which we got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Nobody knew how to chop wood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Nobody knew how to chop trees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But nevertheless, we got used to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we were chopping those trees down until 19-- until the end of 1941.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The trees were simply-- he-- they told us-- by the way, in 1941, they war broke out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that time, we didn't know any-- any-- any war, so the trees, some of them, the smaller trees, were going for coal mines.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were cut, I think, you know, the height of the-- of the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, the height-- the height, I think, was eight feet, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In feet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was about eight feet from the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it called [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to clean that tree-- that tree, strip it from, from the core, you know, which is the outside of the tree.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Completely clean.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And most of it went for telephone poles.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
